<?xml version="1.0"?>

<jpgrotator>

	<parameters>
		<rotatetime>3</rotatetime>
		<randomplay>false</randomplay>
		<shownavigation>true</shownavigation>
		<transition>fluids</transition>
	</parameters>
	
<photos>
<photo path="images/1.jpg" link="http://www.html6game.com/" />
<photo path="images/2.jpg" link="http://www.html6game.com/" />
<photo path="images/3.jpg" link="http://www.html6game.com/" />
<photo path="images/4.jpg" link="http://www.html6game.com/" />
<photo path="images/5.jpg" link="http://www.html6game.com/" />

</photos>

</jpgrotator>


/*****************************************************/

rotatetime：幻灯图片显示间隔：推荐2-10秒最好

randomplay：是否随机播放，true为是，false为否

shownavigation：是否显示数字按钮导航，true为是，false为否

transition：变换效果．共有四种，fade, bgfade, fluids, blocks, circles．

photos标签为图片的路径和链接地址．

/******************************************************/